full_text: Screened by NARA, 9/14/2023 a U.S. Department of Justice Immigration and Naturalization Service COPIES OF DOCUMENTS SUBMITTED ARE EXACT PHOTOCOPIES OF UNALTERED ORIGINAL DOCUMENTS. I UNDERSTAND THAT I MAY BE REQUIRED TO SUBMIT ORIGINAL DOCUMENTS TO AN IMMIGRATION OR CONSULAR OFFICIAL AT A LATER DATE. COPIAS DE LOS DOCUMENTOS INCLUIDOS CON ESTA APLICACION SON COPIAS EXACTAS DE LOS DOCUMENTOS ORIGINALES. COMPRENDO (ENTIENDO) QUE, EN CASO NECESARIO, Y SI ASI LO REQUIEREN EL SERVICIO DE IMMIGRACION 0 EL CONSULADO AMERICANO, TENDRE QUE PRESENTAR LOS DOCUMENTOS ORIGINALES DEBIDAMENTE CERTIFICADOS. X Tara singh Dhesi SIGNATURE (FIRMA) 11 -19.96 X Fara singh Phesi DATE (FECHA) XR-335 1231 (3/18/91)
